2474
2475static void forEachMatch(const SimpleRange& range, const String& target, FindOptions options, const Function<bool(CharacterRange)>& match)
2476{
2477 SearchBuffer buffer(target, options);
2478 if (buffer.needsMoreContext()) {
2479 auto beforeStartRange = SimpleRange { makeBoundaryPointBeforeNodeContents(range.start.document()), range.start };
2480 for (SimplifiedBackwardsTextIterator backwardsIterator(beforeStartRange); !backwardsIterator.atEnd(); backwardsIterator.advance()) {
2481 buffer.prependContext(backwardsIterator.text());
2482 if (!buffer.needsMoreContext())
2483 break;
2484 }
2485 }
2486
2487 CharacterIterator findIterator(range, findIteratorOptions(options));
2488 while (!findIterator.atEnd()) {
2489 findIterator.advance(buffer.append(findIterator.text()));
2490 while (1) {
2491 size_t matchStartOffset;
2492 size_t newMatchLength = buffer.search(matchStartOffset);
2493 if (!newMatchLength) {
2494 if (findIterator.atBreak() && !buffer.atBreak()) {
2495 buffer.reachedBreak();
2496 continue;
2497 }
2498 break;
2499 }
2500 size_t lastCharacterInBufferOffset = findIterator.characterOffset();
2501 ASSERT(lastCharacterInBufferOffset >= matchStartOffset);
2502 if (match(CharacterRange(lastCharacterInBufferOffset - matchStartOffset, newMatchLength)))
2503 return;
2504 }
2505 }
2506}
2507
2508static SimpleRange rangeForMatch(const SimpleRange& range, FindOptions options, CharacterRange match)
2509{
2510 auto noMatchResult = [&] () {
2511 auto& boundary = options.contains(Backwards) ? range.start : range.end;
2512 return SimpleRange { boundary, boundary };
2513 };
2514
2515 if (!match.length)
2516 return noMatchResult();
2517
2518 CharacterIterator it(range, findIteratorOptions(options));
2519
2520 it.advance(match.location);
2521 if (it.atEnd())
2522 return noMatchResult();
2523 auto start = it.range().start;
2524
2525 it.advance(match.length - 1);
2526 if (it.atEnd())
2527 return noMatchResult();
2528
2529 return { WTFMove(start), it.range().end };
2530}
2531
2532SimpleRange findClosestPlainText(const SimpleRange& range, const String& target, FindOptions options, uint64_t targetOffset)
2533{
2534 CharacterRange closestMatch;
2535 uint64_t closestMatchDistance = std::numeric_limits<uint64_t>::max();
2536 forEachMatch(range, target, options, [&] (CharacterRange match) {
2537 auto distance = [] (uint64_t a, uint64_t b) -> uint64_t {
2538 return std::abs(static_cast<int64_t>(a - b));
2539 };
2540 auto matchDistance = std::min(distance(match.location, targetOffset), distance(match.location + match.length, targetOffset));
2541 if (matchDistance > closestMatchDistance)
2542 return false;
2543 if (matchDistance == closestMatchDistance && !options.contains(Backwards))
2544 return false;
2545 closestMatch = match;
2546 if (!matchDistance && !options.contains(Backwards))
2547 return true;
2548 closestMatchDistance = matchDistance;
2549 return false;
2550 });
2551 return rangeForMatch(range, options, closestMatch);
2552}
2553
2554SimpleRange findPlainText(const SimpleRange& range, const String& target, FindOptions options)
2555{
2556 // When searching forward stop since we want the first match.
2557 // When searching backward keep going since we want the last match.
2558 bool stopAfterFindingMatch = !options.contains(Backwards);
2559 CharacterRange lastMatchFound;
2560 forEachMatch(range, target, options, [&] (CharacterRange match) {
2561 lastMatchFound = match;
2562 return stopAfterFindingMatch;
2563 });
2564 return rangeForMatch(range, options, lastMatchFound);

2567bool containsPlainText(const String& document, const String& target, FindOptions options)
2568{
2569 SearchBuffer buffer { target, options };
2570 StringView remainingText { document };
2571 while (!remainingText.isEmpty()) {
2572 size_t charactersAppended = buffer.append(document);
2573 remainingText = remainingText.substring(charactersAppended);
2574 if (remainingText.isEmpty())
2575 buffer.reachedBreak();
2576 size_t matchStartOffset;
2577 if (buffer.search(matchStartOffset))
2578 return true;
2579 }
2580 return false;
